<div id="review_4353721012" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4353721012" />
    <a title="Axl Oswaldo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/117422922-axl-oswaldo"><img alt="Axl Oswaldo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1641969918p2/117422922.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4353721012?book_show_action=true">Nov 23, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Axl Oswaldo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Axl Oswaldo" href="/user/show/117422922-axl-oswaldo">Axl Oswaldo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/19454572-bartleby-the-scrivener">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117422922-axl-oswaldo?shelf=5-star-books">5-star-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117422922-axl-oswaldo?shelf=november-2021">november-2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/117422922-axl-oswaldo?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4353721012" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4381250156502006062"><b>Bartleby, you are my idol!</b><br/><br/>Wow! I think it&apos;s fair to say that this is one of the most meaningful and enjoyable short <i>novellas</i> I&apos;ve read so far. I loved it quite a bit. <br/><br/>If you want to read something short, but significant, please go, and pick this one up – I hope you can enjoy it as much as I did.<br/><br/>…<br/><br/>By the way, if someone asked me whether I will type a complete review of this book or not, well,… <i>
  <b>I would prefer not to.</b>
</i> ;)<br/><br/>Don’t get me wrong, it’s too short that I couldn’t say anything without spoi</span>
  <span id="freeText4381250156502006062" style="display:none"><b>Bartleby, you are my idol!</b><br /><br />Wow! I think it's fair to say that this is one of the most meaningful and enjoyable short <i>novellas</i> I've read so far. I loved it quite a bit. <br /><br />If you want to read something short, but significant, please go, and pick this one up – I hope you can enjoy it as much as I did.<br /><br />…<br /><br />By the way, if someone asked me whether I will type a complete review of this book or not, well,… <i>
  <b>I would prefer not to.</b>
</i> ;)<br /><br />Don’t get me wrong, it’s too short that I couldn’t say anything without spoilers. So, please, trust me and give it a shot. :)<br /><br /><i>
  <b>In answer to my advertisement, a motionless young man one morning, stood upon my office threshold, the door being open, for it was summer. ... pallidly neat, pitiably respectable, incurably forlorn! It was Bartleby.</b>
</i></span>
  <a data-text-id="4381250156502006062" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


